{"tid":1570050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳皓桓指下午會帶同《基本法》以個人身份到銅鑼灣, 基本遊行和集會毋須警方批准。","createTime":"2019-09-15T01:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:14:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4705902e8102edeff63b810e504c35b0adca1b96","tid":1570050,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:18:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1171812&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1171812%26csid%3D261_341&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=46a34950\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1171812&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n陳皓桓指下午會帶同《基本法》以個人身份到銅鑼灣<br />\n15.09.2019 08:56<br />\n<br />\n民陣因警方反對，取消原訂下午的遊行。民陣副召集人陳皓桓在個人社交網站表示，今日下午會以個人身份，帶同《基本法》和穿上公民抗命的衣服到銅鑼灣東角道，以和平、理性和非暴力方式，表達示威者沒有放棄。他指不會稱之為「行街」，因為根據基本法，香港居民享有遊行和示威的自由，基本遊行和集會毋須警方批准。<br />\n<br />\n陳皓桓又表示，明白如果今日公開參與遊行會被拘捕，日後將面對監禁，但他指，眼見前線的年輕人比自己更勇敢，反思是否應該因為身份或懼怕而不實踐自己的理念。"},{"pid":"87d74b6c63ed6be2dc50d9749fbc7d1724c3600c","tid":1570050,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c49bfeea4df0370b509046a280ff0c5bc6217b","tid":1570050,"uid":164517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:19:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e1b5bd38c77d8859083fac8bb71260ba7c7684d","tid":1570050,"uid":272580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:20:10.000Z","msg":"希望佢諮詢過法律意見，同埋有更有份量既人一齊企係度咁講，唔係被拉被打都係滅聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3b2c2fc165cbbf0145e3af52f8b1d1356bbbce","tid":1570050,"uid":164517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img